Jacques Perrin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques_Perrin 0 Jacques Perrin (born Jacques André Simonet; 13 July 1941) is a French actor and filmmaker. He is occasionally credited as Jacques Simonet. Simonet was his father's name and Perrin his mother's. Jacques_Perrin ( born Jacques_André_Simonet ; 13_July_1941 ) is a_French_actor_and_filmmaker .
